('C2', 4049, $$Voz passiva para objetividade$$, $$It was found that...$$, $$ًں”¬$$,
$$Na escrita cientifica/formal, a passiva remove o agente e soa objetiva: 'The experiment was conducted', 'It was found that...', 'Data were collected'. Foca no processo, nao em quem fez.$$,
